<P>"Do you in&s;ult an officer of the Inqui|&s;ition!"
exclaimed the ruffian. "That
holy Community will inform you what
you incur by re&s;i&s;ting it's mandate."</P>
<P>The prie&s;t interrupted Vivaldi's retort,
"If you are really officers of that tremen|dous
